31:49.492 --> 31:52.609
I found microfractures
in the metacarpals...

31:52.703 --> 31:56.992
on the same arm
with the Colles’ fracture.

31:59.043 --> 32:00.999
I love this country,
Dr. Saroyan.

32:01.087 --> 32:04.671
When I said I see
the devil’s face daily—

32:06.342 --> 32:08.549
You know I served
as a translator in Iraq.

32:10.721 --> 32:13.383
Normal day, milk run
to an outlying village
to talk about water,

32:13.516 --> 32:16.849
