took out our Humvee.
Oh, my God.

32:16.936 --> 32:21.430
Two dead, three wounded,
and l was the only one
left conscious.

32:21.524 --> 32:24.266
I’m a translator.
I use words.

32:24.360 --> 32:29.730
But coming towards us
with an AK-47—
an insurgent.

32:29.824 --> 32:32.531
He raised it, intending
to finish us off.

32:32.660 --> 32:35.618
And that was the devil?
No, no.

32:35.704 --> 32:38.116
I shot this man
in the heart.

32:38.207 --> 32:41.699
The devil, that evil—

32:41.794 --> 32:46.083
I saw it in his eyes, sure,
but it was in me, too,
when I pulled that trigger.

32:46.173 --> 32:48.755
You were defending
your unit, Mr. Vaziri.

32:48.843 --> 32:51.880
This man
lay dead at my feet.

32:51.971 --> 32:54.383
I searched his body
for identification...

32:54.473 --> 32:57.965
and I found a photograph
of him with his little boy,

32:58.060 --> 33:01.473
his wife laughing.

33:01.564 --> 33:04.226
A family.

33:04.316 --> 33:07.058
Tell me that the devil
did not win on that day.

33:10.156 --> 33:13.398
You didn’t lose your faith.
You pray five times a day.

33:13.492 --> 33:16.780
l have to believe that Allah
will show me how to live.

33:19.123 --> 33:23.617
I found microfractures
on the maxillary
and mandibular.

33:25.838 --> 33:28.796
He was electrocuted?
The current must have
passed through his hand,

33:28.883 --> 33:31.090
traveled across his body
then out his backside.

33:31.177 --> 33:34.635
It was the muscle spasms
that caused his intestines
to rupture.

33:34.722 --> 33:37.680
I should let Dr. Brennan
know right away.

33:37.766 --> 33:39.722
Of course.

33:42.062 --> 33:44.849
I did... think that—

33:44.940 --> 33:49.775
wonder if you considered us
to be the Great Satan.

33:49.862 --> 33:52.604
- I am familiar with that phrase.
- I know.

33:52.698 --> 33:55.440
l was there when you told
Dr. Hodgins that his T-shirt...

33:55.534 --> 33:58.901
which read
“I am with the Great Satan”...

33:58.996 --> 34:01.282
