a maximum 225 volts, and there’s
a fail-safe mechanism.

34:22.561 --> 34:28.272
Our analysis indicates that
Neal Lowery endured an extended
shock of at least 480 volts.

34:28.359 --> 34:32.477
is there anywhere
in this complex where 480 volts
m/ght be generated?

34:32.571 --> 34:36.029
