at Havenhurst 15 years ago.

34:46.919 --> 34:48.830
All the wiring
and breakers—

34:48.921 --> 34:51.082
there’s nothing more
than 225 volts.

34:51.173 --> 34:55.257
Now, I’m scanning
the original plans,
and they’re from 1908.

34:56.345 --> 34:58.301
Okay.

34:58.389 --> 35:01.426
So, on the original blueprint,
there was a four-wire,

35:01.517 --> 35:04.133
600-volt transformer
in the basement.

35:04.270 --> 35:08.934
