where the old generator is installed
was sealed off.

35:09.024 --> 35:12.061
Except for these
all-access panels.

35:12.152 --> 35:14.359
Yeah, but they’d need those
in case of a fire.

35:14.446 --> 35:16.357
Dr. Copeland said that
Neal Lowery had a knack...

35:16.448 --> 35:18.905
for searching out nooks
and crannies to hide out in.

35:20.744 --> 35:24.362
Okay, the access panel
should be down this
corridor to the left.

35:26.667 --> 35:28.749
Ah, you got to be
kidding me.
Wait.

35:28.836 --> 35:30.042
[Chuckles]

35:30.129 --> 35:32.541
I also have an app
that gives you song titles.

35:32.673 --> 35:34.914
All you have to do
is hum a few notes—
Maybe later, okay?

35:35.009 --> 35:37.000
Okay, it should be
behind all of this.

35:39.013 --> 35:40.173
[ Booth ]
Look at that.

35:40.264 --> 35:42.846
[ Booth ]
Careful.

35:50.024 --> 35:52.731
Check this out.

35:52.818 --> 35:54.809
