36:13.380 --> 36:14.369
Booth?
Yeah.

36:14.465 --> 36:15.875
Oh, my God.

36:15.966 --> 36:17.877
The electrical circuit
must have been completed...

36:17.968 --> 36:20.084
when Neal backed
into this water pipe.

36:21.472 --> 36:23.884
[ Sweets ]
Look what I found.

36:36.904 --> 36:39.316
“Welcome to hell.”

36:51.043 --> 36:53.034
I ran a simulation
of the electrocution...

36:53.128 --> 36:56.165
based on the current
