the equipment at Havenhurst.

36:56.298 --> 36:59.085
Wait. But he’s not dead.
Yeah, I know.

36:59.176 --> 37:02.589
Based on Neal’s age and weight,
plus the clothes he was wearing,

37:02.679 --> 37:04.590
that current would have
thrown h/m clear.

37:04.681 --> 37:08.219
- And he should have survived.
- Plus the muscular
contortions and spasms...

37:08.310 --> 37:11.643
were nowhere near violent
enough to fracture his wrist.

37:11.730 --> 37:13.231
So, then what happened?

37:13.315 --> 37:16.523
What if Neal Lowery wasn’t
wearing his rubber-soled boots?

37:16.610 --> 37:18.726
Okay. Give me a second.

37:18.821 --> 37:21.028
You know, I just don’t
think that someone...

37:21.115 --> 37:25.575
who just shot himself up
with heroin is likely
to, uh, put his boots on.

37:25.702 --> 37:28.159
Why?
Well, ’cause
he’s on the nod.

37:28.247 --> 37:32.331
That means that he, uh, vomits
and succumbs to the euphoria.

37:32.418 --> 37:35.581
Wow. Listen to you,
all street.

37:35.671 --> 37:38.333
Maybe Phillip administered
the heroin to Neal...

37:38.424 --> 37:40.756
as though it were some kind
of legitimate medicine.

37:40.843 --> 37:43.004
No. Between the toes—
that’s not legitimate.

37:43.095 --> 37:46.178
- The guy is crazy, Sweets.
- But he’s consistent.

37:46.265 --> 37:50.508
Phillip operates rationally
behind his delusions.
He believes he’s a doctor.

37:50.602 --> 37:55.096
Angela, can you call up a photo
