39:00.756 --> 39:04.624
It’s not possible.
It’s just not possible.
Gabe wouldn’t kill his brother.

39:04.718 --> 39:09.303
Mrs. Lowery, what you
and your family went through—

39:09.389 --> 39:11.300
it’s almost unbearable.

39:11.391 --> 39:13.973
Gabe loved his brother.
Why would he do
such a thing?

39:14.061 --> 39:17.349
We know that Gabe went to visit
Neal the night he disappeared.

39:17.439 --> 39:19.725
We believe that there was
another patient. . .

39:19.816 --> 39:24.435
named Phillip who told Gabe
about Neal’s hideout
in the basement.

39:25.739 --> 39:27.775
Gabe found Neal
shooting up heroin.

39:28.784 --> 39:31.116
Gabe struck Neal with a pipe.

39:31.203 --> 39:37.164
Neal fell back
into a transformer
and was electrocuted.

39:37.251 --> 39:41.620
But the church?
The burning on the altar?

39:41.713 --> 39:46.582
We all become angry at God
sometimes, Mrs. Lowery.

39:49.096 --> 39:51.758
[ Mrs. Lowery]
Who could blame him ?

39:51.848 --> 39:55.215
Why did God do this to my family?
We were good people.

39:55.310 --> 39:57.926
And then—

39:58.021 --> 40:00.103
this.

40:01.275 --> 40:03.266
I’m sorry for your pain.

40:03.360 --> 40:05.476
You—

40:06.738 --> 40:08.649
You can’t even
imagine my pain.

40:30.846 --> 40:33.713
[ Brennan ]
I need to ask you
some things.

40:33.807 --> 40:36.765
You gonna ask me
about God and the devil?

40:36.852 --> 40:38.513
Yes.

40:38.604 --> 40:42.472
You’re gonna ask me
how God can place
such a burden on good people.

40:42.566 --> 40:48.311
No. I’m going to ask you how
you still believe in a kind god
after a case like this.

40:48.405 --> 40:51.147
Is my faith shaken?

40:51.241 --> 40:54.074
Yeah. Mm-hmm. It is.

40:54.161 --> 40:56.152
It is?

40:56.246 --> 40:59.113
Yeah. I’ll go home tonight
and I’ll lie in bed...

40:59.207 --> 41:04.577
and I’ll toss and I’ll turn
and I’ll beat myself up,

41:04.671 --> 41:07.003
and,uh,
I’ll question everything.

41:07.132 --> 41:11.045
Will you get
your faith back?
Always have in the past.

41:11.136 --> 41:14.720
So, you have faith that you
will retain your faith?

41:16.099 --> 41:18.010
Why?

41:18.101 --> 41:21.093
Because, Bones,

41:21.188 --> 41:23.930
the sun will come up,
and tomorrow’s a new day.

41:26.693 --> 41:29.070
I know that feeling.
[ Chuckles ]

41:29.196 --> 41:31.187
Really?
Mm-hmm.

41:31.281 --> 41:34.114
You know what it feels like
to get your faith back?

41:34.201 --> 41:37.614
When I see effects and I’m
unable to discern the cause,

41:37.704 --> 41:41.117
my faith in reason
and consequences is shaken.

41:42.209 --> 41:44.291
Then what happens?

41:45.629 --> 41:47.585
Two plus two equals four.

41:48.882 --> 41:52.124
I put sugar in my coffee,
and it tastes sweet.

41:52.219 --> 41:56.713
The sun comes up
because the world turns.

41:58.183 --> 42:00.094
These things
are beautiful to me.

42:02.354 --> 42:05.846
There are mysteries
I will never understand.

42:05.941 --> 42:09.058
But everywhere I look,

42:09.152 --> 42:12.019
| see proof that for every effect...

42:12.114 --> 42:14.730
there is a corresponding cause,

42:14.825 --> 42:17.908
even if! can’t see it.

42:17.994 --> 42:20.155
| find that reassuring.

42:21.206 --> 42:23.117
And life is good again.

42:23.208 --> 42:25.745
[ Chuckles ]
